Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真心灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使我成为完全的我的纯真心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快收集过来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们沉默的救世主啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们优秀的部下 正在策划著作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您再忍耐一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意地回头看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉似乎有人在叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然地绽放淡淡的不安之花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 下一首曲子是各位等待已久的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是荒木仁太的新曲"忧郁的危机之爱"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0){\fn方正粗圆_GBK}{\fs45}{\pos(320,450)}{\b0}{\1c&HD7FFFF&}{\4c&HFFC1C1&}{\shad1}{\bord0}最喜欢当偶像 烦恼的米美特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像砂糖上的蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们除了追星 就没别的事好做吗?…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指追着偶像跑哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着然后做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也做不了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂这些人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 美奈子?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在发呆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说我们会追星这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 美奈 荒木仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明年就是高中生了 追星这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是 还有考试呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真心话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明年七月公开预定 我主演的电影里的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想从大家中间挑选出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公开试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一场会从明天下午四点半开始 在港区文化会馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装审查也有 自满的泳装也不要忘记带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年的夏天 与我ㄧ起强烈燃烧吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女主角…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们沉默的救世主 已经等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的作战有在进行吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 教授 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请看这个 这是这次的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木仁太 笑容最灿烂的十八岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推出的新唱片 忧郁危机之爱 人气上升中!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去成为第一的闪亮歌手是迟早的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌星吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特…总觉得你只瞄准有名人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的和兴趣混在一起的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们死亡幻影中是无法出头的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只选择有名人是因为 魅力高的人的心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得对新的救世主的觉醒最有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特要哭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 米美特 用不着哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是对前途有望的你担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也都拜托你了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日的大干部是米美特 是你哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特会加油的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的干…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"喜欢 喜欢 荒木!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"最喜欢皮肤晒成小麦色的你!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个x代入这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔 好厉害! 亏你能懂呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…美奈呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说感冒了 在家里睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是想看一眼真正的荒木…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就是他的迷!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木…荒木先生何时会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的试镜不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的复选 才做为嘉宾出席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为能见一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木刚出道时的官方T恤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相都有怨气在身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爱野美奈子 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是米美…不 是美美 羽生美美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然人类要对自己喜欢的东西全力追求!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下面一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是! 爱野美奈子!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有朝气的初中3年生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特技是空中回旋接球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧本中我想也有吻戏 你会怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会对父母隐瞒演戏这件事!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果合格了 被监督邀请吃饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 我不挑食的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端出来的任何东西都吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…只有对蘑菇比较不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羽生美美…啊…美美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你参加这个试镜的动机是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来就行…冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…嗯…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在发表第一回审查的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的合格者是以下五位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有五个人能合格啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大可能了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要见一眼荒木…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,251号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,252号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格者请到前面来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人会接受明天的第二次审查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 如同我们较早通知你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试镜最后的优胜者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会扮演在下个夏天上映的电影中的角色…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天合格的话怎么办…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好真的会合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一定会合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的容貌 出众的身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 米美特大人 是不会输给人类的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 你来了!米美特好高兴~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米美特…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有点发烧…眼睛还充血了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热心工作是很好 但身体也要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种优秀的人才请假了 我会很心疼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须夺取荒木的纯真心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样的话 荒木会死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的荒木会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好这次的试镜 会当做没发生过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的职业道路也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…不袭击荒木的话 我会变成叛徒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就能拿到最高干部的地位了的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你期待很高…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然人类要对自己喜欢的东西全力追求!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡幻影会怎么样和我没关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和荒木一起在夏天燃烧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了荒木君 这种背叛组织的事做给你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我就是做不来坏事的 天生的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主角的荣冠 到底会是谁拿到…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 也请在场的大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之八十的人支持的人就是这次试镜合格者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 最初的一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔忒弥斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 为什么在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像美奈的作风…向大家保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得追着荒木这件事变的难以开口…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请按按钮!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…很遗憾!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面请六十八号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下下个就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像美少女战士就要诞生了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早吃了最喜欢的煎蛋来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来 想要成为 什么角色都能担当的大女演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为大女演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为女演员 什么事情都做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为女演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一位 251号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,251号 爱野美奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港区芝公园中学三年生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真小…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是可惜!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一位 请…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像美少女战士的梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是见到荒木了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果可惜了 但还会有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木…我从现在开始到永远都会为你加油的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你总有一天会把我忘掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到时候都会把我忘掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把我忘掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢过我的那种心情还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像毕业后 只怀着喜欢的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人才会知道真正的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在请大力支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想就这么成为偶像结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今早吃了最喜欢的煎蛋来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来要成为 什么角色都能担当的大女演员…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的挑战者 请按按钮!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太遗憾了 这次变成没有合格者的结果了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽生 不要紧吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是死亡幻影的米美特!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加这个试镜是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取在那里的荒木仁太的纯真心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 戴蒙 歌姬!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光炮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被我的魅力 闪亮闪亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很痛苦的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…在闪亮闪亮着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 干掉他!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:28.71,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}Moon Tiara Action
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会疼的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.90,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}唱的是你 听的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.29,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}歌曲是大家的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.16,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}袭击偶像的坏家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.99,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}我们爱与正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.34,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}水手队伍!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:48.78,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}要代表月亮惩罚你!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:58.28,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}金星星光力量 变身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.29,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}米美特!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:25.51,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}装成歌迷袭击荒木的你 是歌迷的敌人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:27.54,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}全世界偶像的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.11,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}水手金星!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:34.55,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}要用爱的神罚来惩罚你!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有装!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是五魔女的米美特!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你对荒木真的…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话荒木的心永远是我们的东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追星也有追星的规矩!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给喜欢的偶像添麻烦是不行的 真是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒木会死的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那是当然的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡幻影是邪恶的组织!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬 用你的杀人之歌把她们都杀了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的歌声是从发声练习开始的 请稍等片刻~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人之歌!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌词忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 水手月亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
